Hey does anyone know why a spark max would flash green/white (which is forward limit) when there is no limit switch plugged in? Motor won’t move forward at all. There was a limit switch on it that worked before but it’s been completely removed now.

Update:
If we disable the limit switches then it works but we’d like to run the limit switches so it’s like something fried inside.

Factory default is normally open.
